WEBVTT

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:30.976
the larger the neocortex,

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.976
the more likely it is to be deceptive.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.976
Now you might remember Koko.

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:38.239
Does anybody remember Koko the gorilla
who was taught sign language?

00:05:38.263 --> 00:05:40.976
Koko was taught to communicate
via sign language.

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:42.976
Here's Koko with her kitten.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:45.976
It's her cute little, fluffy pet kitten.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:49.976
Koko once blamed her pet kitten
for ripping a sink out of the wall.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.976
(Laughter)

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:54.191
We're hardwired to become
leaders of the pack.

00:05:54.215 --> 00:05:55.976
It's starts really, really early.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:57.976
How early?

00:05:58.000 --> 00:05:59.976
Well babies will fake a cry,

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:01.976
pause, wait to see who's coming